erver components and functions.</p></div><div class="text-center"><h4 class="mb-2 heading-3xl font-black">Finally, a backend that works like your frontend</h4><p class="text-lg text-palette-green12">Expo Hosting lets you move fast, stay flexible, and build with confidence all without waiting on backend teams.</p></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-y-16"><div class="grid grid-cols-2 items-center gap-x-12 gap-y-16 text-lg opacity-0 max-md:flex max-md:flex-col-reverse"><div><p class="mb-2 text-2xl font-black">Simplify your backend flow</p><p class="text-base">Handle auth, retries, and API chaos in one edge-deployed layer. Hosting acts as your API gateway, BFF, and middleware—no infra, no handoffs, just clean backend logic, where and when you need it.</p></div><img src="/static/images/eas-hosting/hosting-tile1.png" alt="EAS Hosting tile 1"/></div><div class="grid grid-cols-2 items-center gap-x-12 gap-y-16 text-lg opacity-0 max-md:flex max-md:flex-col"><img src="/static/images/eas-hosting/hosting-tile2.png" alt="EAS Hosting tile 2"/><div><p class="mb-2 text-2xl font-black">Ship backend logic at frontend speed</p><p class="text-base">Deploy APIs and server logic with the same CLI you use to build your app. No waiting on infra. No devops hurdles. Just write code and ship.</p></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-2 items-center gap-x-12 gap-y-16 text-lg opacity-0 max-md:flex max-md:flex-col-reverse"><div><p class="mb-2 text-2xl font-black">Reliability without manual overhead</p><p class="text-base">Observable by default. Immutable deploys. Automatic scaling. Hosting gives you consistent, low-latency performance—without managing servers or worrying about versioning.</p></div><img src="/static/images/eas-hosting/hosting-tile3.png" alt="EAS Hosting tile 3"/></div><div class="grid grid-cols-2 items-center gap-x-12 gap-y-16 text-lg opacity-0 max-md:flex max-md:flex-col"><img src="/static/images/eas-hosting/hosting-tile4.png" alt="EAS Hosting tile 4"/><div><p class="mb-2 text-2xl font-black">One command. Live everywhere</p><p class="text-base">Global edge runtime lets you launch backend logic in seconds with Hosting. Integrated with Expo Application Services for a seamless, scalable path from dev to deploy.</p></div></div></div><h4 class="mt-6 text-center heading-2xl font-black">Trusted by teams shipping faster with less overhead</h4><div class="inline-block" style="transform-style:preserve-3d"><div class="opacity-0"><div class="mx-auto flex max-w-screen-md flex-col gap-5 rounded-2xl border-[5px] border-[#648B5999] border-double bg-[#0e151266] px-6 py-8 text-center shadow-xl"><q class="text-xl">We had four days, two people, one mission and - thanks to Expo - one codebase. Having our mobile app, website and serverless functions in one place was the only way we could&#x27;ve pulled it off.</q><p class="text-lg font-bold text-palette-green12">Reed Harmyer, CEO, Skylight Social</p></div></div></div><h4 class="mt-6 text-center heading-3xl font-black">See how Hosting fits into the full Expo flow</h4><div class="flex flex-col gap-12"><div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-12 max-md:grid-cols-1"><div><div><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://expo.dev/blog/deploying-an-expo-app-to-web-with-eas-hosting"><div class="border-secondary bg-default overflow-hidden border-[#648B59]! border-2 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 mx-auto aspect-video rounded-lg hocus:scale-[1.02] hocus:border-[#79C564]!"><img src="/static/images/eas-hosting/hosting-blog-post.avif" alt="Deploy an Expo app to web in 2 commands with EAS Hosting"/></div><p class="mt-6 text-center font-semibold">Deploy an Expo app to web in two commands with EAS Hosting</p></a></div></div><div><div><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://youtube.com/watch?v=2_UzR1wdimI"><div class="border-secondary bg-default overflow-hidden border-[#648B59]! border-2 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 mx-auto aspect-video rounded-lg hocus:scale-[1.02] hocus:border-[#79C564]